sections.content:
Registration and bookings: name, phone, email, hotel address, check-in/out dates, messaging accounts (LINE, WhatsApp, WeChat);
Planning: travel preferences (schedules, locations, special requirements), payment methods and records (cash, USDT);
Customer service interaction: contact records, inquiries and responses, IP, browser type, and usage logs.

We use your personal information only for:
Service provision: booking confirmation, coordination, transfers, and assistance;
Quality improvement: satisfaction surveys, internal improvements, and training;
Support: problem resolution and immediate assistance;
Marketing (with consent): promotions and event news.

With your consent, we may share information with:
Providers: transportation companies, hotels, private clubs;
Payment processors: for USDT transactions and currency conversion;
Authorities: when required by law;
Others with your consent.
All partners sign confidentiality agreements and use data only for agreed purposes.

Technical protection: SSL/TLS encryption, firewalls, and security scans;
Access control: only authorized personnel with two-factor authentication;
Retention period: booking and transaction data kept for up to 3 years;
Deletion requests: you may request data deletion or correction at any time.
